To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AccumulationDistribution _ad;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_ad = AD(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_ad.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "accumulationdistribution", _ad.Current.Value);
}
